      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;hdoj6438buy-and-resell&#34;&gt;[hdoj6438]Buy and Resell&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;题意&#34;&gt;题意&lt;/h2&gt;
